dalam ketukan tiga-empat.

395
00:26:01,895 --> 00:26:04,064
Kuat-lemah-lemah.

396
00:26:04,164 --> 00:26:06,066
Dia sangat logis,

397
00:26:06,166 --> 00:26:07,935
hampir seperti profesor kecil.

398
00:26:08,769 --> 00:26:10,804
