00:27:09,530 --> 00:27:11,865
Tunggu sebentar.

416
00:27:13,567 --> 00:27:15,903
Kau masih belum memperbaiki
lampu itu?

417
00:27:16,003 --> 00:27:17,204
Kau bisa tersandung.

418
00:27:17,304 --> 00:27:18,372
Hati-hati.

419
00:27:18,705 --> 00:27:21,208
Buka pintunya, Sayang.

420
00:27:21,875 --> 00:27:23,644
